snippet.title: The Angry Hippie
snippet.description:
This channel is NOT monetized. This channel is meant to be a bridge between the complex nature of reality and the average person who is just beginning their journey of self-discovery. I have rendered complex philosophies, ideologies and sciences -- into bite sized formats, for anyone to understand and learn. The Species with Amnesia Series in particular, is a synthesis of many great minds -- who speak of the solutions to the current problem with the world -- combined into a singular voice that speaks to the viewer. 

I hope you enjoy.
